    Let test1 be run_test("Duplicate Extension Point", test_duplicate_extension_point)
    Append test1 to results
    
    Note: Test invalid extension registration
    Let test2 be run_test("Invalid Extension", test_invalid_extension)
    Append test2 to results
    
